reviews.text: Very small place to accommodate lots of locals. Quick breakfast and lunch are served.
Great old local restaurant. Foods taste not bad too
Traditional Hong Kong restaurant providing great local food, but you cannot expect high level of services.
small local business with tasty food and old-fashioned style!!

I love this place! The staff are friendly, the food is delicious and affordable - though to be honest, I'd pay more than what they charge for their French toast. Overall, it's one of my favorite stops in Hong Kong.

懷舊的玻璃門，窄小的枱櫈，容納不下兩個健碩男子。 橙色嘅意大利粉放在40年前印象的膠碟內，公司三文治中有中式义燒，玻璃樽裝朱古力奶，值得保留嘅茶餐廳
很多人想享受下懷舊茶餐廳，此間雖舊亦合襯，但食品都很一般。
食物及服務都屬一般。只因就腳及相熟
第一次去，可以說是傳統的早餐嗎？東西吃起來平常，大概習慣了台式早餐店的口味:)
幫襯多年，水準保持一流
